text: São Paulo Catarina Executive Airport , is a general aviation airport serving São Paulo Metropolitan Area, Brazil. It is owned and operated by JHSF Participações. ==History== The airport is dedicated to general aviation. It was commissioned on December 16, 2019. ==Airlines and destinations== No scheduled flights operate at this airport. ==Access== The airport is located from downtown São Roque and from downtown São Paulo. ==See also== *List of airports in Brazil ==References== ==External links== * * * * Category:Airports in São Paulo (state) Category:Airports established in 2019
title: São Paulo Catarina Executive Airport
